msgstr "要執行此操作，請前往 :menuselection:`Odoo 主Dashboard --> 開支`，並導航至 *開支* 應用程式。"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/expense.rst:42
msgid ""
"Then, from the *Expenses* dashboard, click :guilabel:`New` to reveal a blank"
